    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>Magma Surges prefer to burrow beneath a battlefield and surface under enemy clusters when Lava Splash is ready. On the surface they are slow, relying on Heat Aura and raw Strength rather than positioning. A Summoner who needs area denial rather than precision will find them effective. One who needs something mobile will find them frustrating.</p>"
